OL,3,CFormer West Ham striker faces trial
OL,4,Cover motoring conviction
OL,6,FFormer West Ham striker Michail
OL,7,FAntonio has had a conviction for a
OL,8,Fmotoring-related offence set aside
OL,9,Fafter telling a court he almost died
OL,10,Fin a car crash.
OL,12,FA judge sitting at Birmingham
OL,13,FMagistrates' Court decided to remove
OL,14,FAntonio's conviction for failing to
OL,15,Fgive information in April 2025 about
OL,16,Fthe driver of a Lamborghini Urus which
OL,17,Fwas clocked speeding in the city
OL,18,Fduring the previous month.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
