PN,37102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781874674
OL,3,CFormer West Ham striker faces trial
OL,4,Cover motoring conviction
OL,6,FAntonio, who had been convicted in his
OL,7,Fabsence in April this year, told the
OL,8,Fjudge on Friday that he had given the
OL,9,Fvehicle to a car company in January
OL,10,Flast year for them to arrange a sale.
OL,12,FThe 36-year-old told the court: "Can I
OL,13,Ftell you the whole situation?
OL,15,F"I almost died in a car crash on the
OL,16,F7th of December 2025.
OL,18,F"On the 1st of March I wasn't even
OL,19,Fphysically driving at the time because
OL,20,FI broke my femur ` I wasn't allowed to
OL,21,Fdrive."
OL,26,@tD@aOUwD@AOUzD@AOU}D@GO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781874674
OL,3,CFormer West Ham striker faces trial
OL,4,Cover motoring conviction
OL,6,FTelling the court his partner had sent
OL,7,Fa letter from the authorities to the
OL,8,Fcar sale firm and told them to sort it
OL,9,Fout, Antonio, who has been playing in
OL,10,Fthe Qatari league, added: "We got a
OL,11,Fsummons for court in September.
OL,13,F"I don't think I was around.
OL,15,F"I was trying to focus on my actual
OL,16,Fcareer and my life. I didn't think
OL,17,Fabout anything outside of that."
OL,26,@rD@[OUuD@AOUwD@AOUyD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
