OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781874674
OL,3,CFormer West Ham striker faces trial
OL,4,Cover motoring conviction
OL,6,FThe single judge hearing the case
OL,7,Fresponded to Antonio's remarks by
OL,8,Fgiving him the opportunity to appeal
OL,9,Fto the Crown Court or for his
OL,10,Fconviction to be set aside.
OL,12,FAntonio, who has also played for
OL,13,FReading, Nottingham Forest,
OL,14,FSouthampton and Sheffield Wednesday,
OL,15,Fopted to plead not guilty and will now
OL,16,Fface trial at the same court on March
OL,17,F2 next year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,372,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F371A1781874674
OL,3,CFormer West Ham striker faces trial
OL,4,Cover motoring conviction
OL,6,FNear the end of the short hearing,
OL,7,FAntonio asked if the press were
OL,8,Fallowed to be present and was then
OL,9,Fasked by the judge if he was famous.
OL,11,FAntonio answered: "Yeah, I am a
OL,12,Ffootballer. I used to play for West
OL,13,FHam."
OL,15,FA charge of speeding relating to the
OL,16,FLamborghini, which was recorded doing
OL,17,Fan average of 50mph in a 40mph zone in
OL,18,FBirmingham on March 1 2025, was
OL,19,Fdropped by prosecutors at a previous
OL,20,Fhearing.
OL,26,@sD@SOUuD@EO]
